<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Jade 初次課程｜Abby Eat Life</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500&family=Playfair+Display:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --sage: #8B9E7E;
  --terra: #C17F59;
  --cream: #FDFBF7;
  --bark: #3D3229;
  --sage-light: #e8ede5;
  --terra-light: #f5e6db;
  --bg: #FDFBF7;
  --bg-secondary: #f3f0ea;
  --border: rgba(61,50,41,0.12);
  --border-md: rgba(61,50,41,0.22);
  --text: #2a2218;
  --text-secondary: #6b5e52;
  --text-tertiary: #a0948a;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
}
* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.page-header {
  background: var(--bark);
  color: var(--cream);
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 16px;
}
.page-header h1 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
}
.page-header .sub {
  font-size: 13px;
  opacity: 0.65;
  margin-top: 2px;
}
.header-dot {
  width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--sage);
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; color: #fff;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.layout { display: flex; min-height: calc(100vh - 72px); }

.sidebar {
  width: 200px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  background: #fff;
  border-right: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  padding: 1.25rem 0;
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  height: calc(100vh - 72px);
  overflow-y: auto;
}
.sidebar-group { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.sidebar-group-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--text-tertiary);
  padding: 0.5rem 1.25rem 0.25rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.sidebar-btn {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
  width: 100%; padding: 8px 1.25rem;
  background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;
  font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-secondary);
  text-align: left; transition: all 0.15s;
}
.sidebar-btn:hover { background: var(--bg-secondary); color: var(--text); }
.sidebar-btn.active {
  background: var(--sage-light);
  color: var(--sage);
  font-weight: 500;
}
.sidebar-btn .badge {
  width: 20px; height: 20px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.badge-a { background: var(--sage-light); color: var(--sage); }
.badge-b { background: var(--terra-light); color: var(--terra); }
.sidebar-btn.active .badge-a { background: var(--sage); color: #fff; }
.sidebar-btn.active .badge-b { background: var(--terra); color: #fff; }

.main {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 2rem;
  max-width: 780px;
}

.section { display: none; }
.section.visible { display: block; }

.section-header {
  display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}
.section-badge {
  width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  color: var(--text);
}

.card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 1.1rem 1.3rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.card-label {
  font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-tertiary);
  margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase;
}

.grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(130px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

.metric-card {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
}
.metric-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.metric-value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text); }
.metric-note { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 2px; }

.chart-wrap { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 200px; margin: 0.75rem 0; }

.tag {
  display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 10px; margin: 2px;
}
.tag-ok { background: var(--sage-light); color: #5a7a4e; }
.tag-warn { background: #fef3e2; color: #a06010; }
.tag-alert { background: #fdecea; color: #a03030; }

.progress-row { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.progress-label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.progress-label span:first-child { color: var(--text-secondary); }
.progress-label span:last-child { color: var(--text); font-weight: 500; }
.progress-bar-bg { height: 8px; background: var(--bg-secondary); border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; }
.progress-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 4px; }
.progress-note { font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-tertiary); margin-top: 3px; }

.info-row {
  display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 14px;
}
.info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.info-icon { color: var(--text-tertiary); flex-shrink: 0; padding-top: 2px; font-size: 16px; }
.info-text { color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; }
.info-text strong { font-weight: 500; }

.compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13px; table-layout: fixed; }
.compare-table th {
  background: var(--bg-secondary);
  font-weight: 500; padding: 8px 12px; text-align: left;
  color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 12px;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}
.compare-table td {
  padding: 9px 12px; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--text); vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.5;
}
.compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
.hl-red { color: #c0392b; font-weight: 500; }
.hl-green { color: #27ae60; font-weight: 500; }

.tip-box {
  background: var(--sage-light);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--sage);
  border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
}
.warn-box {
  background: var(--terra-light);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--terra);
  border-radius: 0 var(--radius-md) var(--radius-md) 0;
  padding: 10px 14px; font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65;
  margin-top: 0.75rem;
}

.week-goal {
  display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 14px;
}
.week-goal:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.goal-num {
  width: 26px; height: 26px; border-radius: 50%;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  background: var(--sage-light); color: var(--sage);
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px;
}
.goal-text { color: var(--text); line-height: 1.55; }
.goal-sub { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 12px; margin-top: 2px; }

.food-chip {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
  padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 12px; margin: 3px;
}
.chip-warn { background: #fef3e2; color: #a06010; }
.chip-bad { background: #fdecea; color: #a03030; }
.chip-ok { background: var(--sage-light); color: #5a7a4e; }

.divider { height: 0.5px; background: var(--border); margin: 1.25rem 0; }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .layout { flex-direction: column; }
  .sidebar { width: 100%; height: auto; position: static; border-right: none; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; padding: 0.5rem; gap: 4px; }
  .sidebar-group { margin: 0; }
  .sidebar-group-label { display: none; }
  .sidebar-btn { border-radius: 20px; padding: 6px 12px; }
  .sidebar-btn.active { background: var(--sage); color: #fff; }
  .main { padding: 1rem; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-header">
  <div class="header-dot">J</div>
  <div>
    <h1>Jade 初次課程</h1>
    <div class="sub">2026.05.25 ｜ Abby Eat Life 營養coaching</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="layout">
  <nav class="sidebar" role="navigation" aria-label="課程模組">
    <div class="sidebar-group">
      <div class="sidebar-group-label">基礎內容</div>
      <button class="sidebar-btn active" onclick="show('a1', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-a">A1</span> 現況盤點
      </button>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('a2', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-a">A2</span> 合理速度
      </button>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('a3', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-a">A3</span> 熱量目標
      </button>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('a4', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-a">A4</span> 紀錄方式
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="sidebar-group">
      <div class="sidebar-group-label">針對性內容</div>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('b1', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-b">B1</span> 水腫成因
      </button>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('b2', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-b">B2</span> 蛋白質策略
      </button>
      <button class="sidebar-btn" onclick="show('b3', this)">
        <span class="badge badge-b">B3</span> 外食陷阱
      </button>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="main">

    <!-- A1 -->
    <div class="section visible" id="sec-a1">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge badge-a">A1</div>
        <div class="section-title">你現在在哪裡？——現況盤點</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-4">
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">週平均體重</div>
          <div class="metric-value">74.1 kg</div>
          <div class="metric-note">5/19–5/24</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">週內波動</div>
          <div class="metric-value">2.0 kg</div>
          <div class="metric-note">73.2 → 75.2</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">目標體重</div>
          <div class="metric-value">65 kg</div>
          <div class="metric-note">差距約 9 kg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">估算每日熱量</div>
          <div class="metric-value">1,600–1,800</div>
          <div class="metric-note">kcal（含外食隱藏油脂）</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">這週體重曲線</div>
        <div class="chart-wrap">
          <canvas id="weightChart" role="img" aria-label="Jade 5月19日至24日體重折線圖，週末因高鈉飲食升至75.2公斤">週間體重：74, 73.2, 73.4, 73.9, 75.2, 74.6</canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="warn-box">週六（5/23）麻辣鍋底＋深夜吃，體重跳至 75.2 kg → 鈉攝取與進食時間是主因，不代表真正長了脂肪</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">三大營養素落點（5天均值估算）</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
          <div class="progress-row">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>蛋白質</span><span>65–80 g（目標 95 g）</span></div>
            <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:72%; background:var(--sage);"></div></div>
            <div class="progress-note">明顯不足，是本階段首要改善項目</div>
          </div>
          <div class="progress-row">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>碳水化合物</span><span>130–160 g</span></div>
            <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:55%; background:#8AAFC4;"></div></div>
            <div class="progress-note">量適中，品質有提升空間（精製 vs 複合碳水）</div>
          </div>
          <div class="progress-row">
            <div class="progress-label"><span>脂肪</span><span>45–60 g（外食低估風險）</span></div>
            <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:65%; background:var(--terra);"></div></div>
            <div class="progress-note">實際可能更高，外食炸物油脂難估</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">目前飲食的亮點 vs 可優化處</div>
        <div style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px;">
          <span class="tag tag-ok">✓ 每天有水煮蛋</span>
          <span class="tag tag-ok">✓ 飯量有控制</span>
          <span class="tag tag-ok">✓ 有蔬菜意識</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="tag tag-warn">△ 蛋白質不足</span>
          <span class="tag tag-warn">△ 高鈉頻率高</span>
          <span class="tag tag-alert">✗ 進食時間不穩</span>
          <span class="tag tag-alert">✗ 外食油脂難估</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- A2 -->
    <div class="section" id="sec-a2">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge badge-a">A2</div>
        <div class="section-title">合理的減重速度是多少？</div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">安全減重速度</div>
          <div class="metric-value">0.5–1%</div>
          <div class="metric-note">體重/週，即每週約 0.4–0.7 kg</div>
        </div>
        <div class="metric-card">
          <div class="metric-label">Jade 的合理預期</div>
          <div class="metric-value">10–16 週</div>
          <div class="metric-note">抵達 65 kg 區間</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">預估體重下降時程</div>
        <div class="chart-wrap">
          <canvas id="progressChart" role="img" aria-label="Jade體重下降預估折線圖，從74公斤在12-16週內降至65公斤左右">預估10-16週可達65kg目標</canvas>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">為什麼不能更快？</div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-icon">⚠</div>
          <div class="info-text"><strong>肌肉流失風險</strong>：每週超過 1% 體重，身體開始分解肌肉當能量，代謝率下降</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-icon">⚠</div>
          <div class="info-text"><strong>代謝適應</strong>：過度熱量赤字會讓身體進入「節能模式」，後期越來越難瘦</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <div class="info-icon">⚠</div>
          <div class="info-text"><strong>反彈風險</strong>：過快減重多為水分＋肌肉，停止後極易回彈</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-box">體重的波動是正常的！每週看「平均值」比每天看數字更有意義。</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- A3 -->
    <div class="section" id="sec-a3">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-badge badge-a">A3</div>
        <div class="section-title">減重期該吃多少？</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">TDEE 估算結果（課堂填寫）</div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:14px;">
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:140px;">🧮 BMR（基礎代謝）</span>
            <input type="number" id="bmr" placeholder="填入數字" oninput="calcTDEE()" style="width:120px; padding:6px 10px; border:0.5px solid var(--border-md); border-radius:var(--radius-md); font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);">
            <span style="color:var(--text-tertiary); font-size:13px;">kcal</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:140px;">⚡ 活動係數</span>
            <select id="activity" onchange="calcTDEE()" style="width:180px; padding:6px 10px; border:0.5px solid var(--border-md); border-radius:var(--radius-md); font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);">
              <option value="1.2">1.2 久坐少動</option>
              <option value="1.375">1.375 輕度活動</option>
              <option value="1.55" selected>1.55 中度活動</option>
              <option value="1.725">1.725 高度活動</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:140px;">🔥 TDEE</span>
            <div id="tdee-display" style="font-size:20px; font-weight:500; color:var(--text); min-width:80px;">——</div>
            <span style="color:var(--text-tertiary); font-size:13px;">kcal／天</span>
          </div>
          <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; font-size:14px;">
            <span style="color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:140px;">🎯 減重目標熱量</span>
            <div id="target-display" style="font-size:20px; font-weight:500; color:var(--sage); min-width:80px;">——</div>
            <span style="color:var(--text-tertiary); font-size:13px;">kcal（赤字 400–500）</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-label">三大營養素目標（填入每日克數）</div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:16px;">
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:6px;">
              <span style="font-size:14px; color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:100px;">🥩 蛋白質</span>
              <input type="number" id="prot-g" placeholder="克數" oninput="calcMacros()" style="width:90px; padding:6px 10px; border:0.5px solid var(--border-md); border-radius:var(--radius-md); font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);">
              <span style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-tertiary);">g　= <span id="prot-kcal" style="color:var(--sage); font-weight:500;">——</span> kcal</span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div id="prot-bar" class="progress-fill" style="width:0%; background:var(--sage); transition:width 0.4s;"></div></div>
            <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-tertiary); margin-top:3px;">約佔總熱量 22–25%　目前僅達 65–80 g，需提升</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:6px;">
              <span style="font-size:14px; color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:100px;">🫒 脂肪</span>
              <input type="number" id="fat-g" placeholder="克數" oninput="calcMacros()" style="width:90px; padding:6px 10px; border:0.5px solid var(--border-md); border-radius:var(--radius-md); font-family:inherit; font-size:14px; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);">
              <span style="font-size:13px; color:var(--text-tertiary);">g　= <span id="fat-kcal" style="color:var(--terra); font-weight:500;">——</span> kcal</span>
            </div>
            <div class="progress-bar-bg"><div id="fat-bar" class="progress-fill" style="width:0%; background:var(--terra); transition:width 0.4s;"></div></div>
            <div style="font-size:11px; color:var(--text-tertiary); margin-top:3px;">約佔總熱量 25–30%　維持荷爾蒙與飽足感的下限</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; margin-bottom:6px;">
              <span style="font-size:14px; color:var(--text-secondary); min-width:100px;">🍚 碳水化合物</span>
